    <p>
      This is an unofficial package. Issues with it should not be reported to GDLauncher upstream!
    </p>
    <p>
      Main Features
    </p>
    <p>
      Modern and easy to use UI
    </p>
    <p>
      Our main focus is to provide a powerful launcher, but keeping the UI clean and modern
    </p>
    <p>
      Browse and Download CurseForge&apos;s Modpacks
    </p>
    <p>
      You&apos;ll be able to browse and download any modpack directly from within the launcher!
    </p>
    <p>
      Support for Vanilla, Forge and Fabric
    </p>
    <p>
      You can play vanilla, forge and fabric directly from the launcher, without needing to download anything else.
    </p>
    <p>
      Built in mods manager
    </p>
    <p>
      You can easily download mods and keep them up to date
    </p>
    <p>
      Auto java setup
    </p>
    <p>
      You don&apos;t need to have java installed on your pc. We will automatically download the best java release to ensure complete compatibility
    </p>
